## 📋 build check commands

| build tool | command | purpose |
|------------|---------|---------|
| **npm** | `npm run build` | build the application for production |
| **yarn** | `yarn build` | build the application for production |
| **maven** | `mvn clean install` | compile, test, and package the application |
| **gradle** | `gradle build` | build the application and run tests |
| **docker** | `docker build .` | build a docker image |

## 📋 test check commands

| test runner | command | purpose |
|-------------|---------|---------|
| **jest** | `npm test` | run all unit and integration tests |
| **mocha** | `npm test` | run all tests |
| **pytest** | `pytest` | run all python tests |
| **junit** | `mvn test` | run all java tests |
| **cypress** | `npm run cypress:run` | run all end-to-end tests |

## ✅ verification complete

if the build succeeds and all tests pass, the build and test qa checks are complete.

